<subSubSection pageId="112" pageNumber="113" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="112.[189,292,563,589]" box="[189,292,563,589]" pageId="112" pageNumber="113">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,292,563,589]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="112" pageNumber="113" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,292,563,589]" pageId="112" pageNumber="113">Remark</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="112.[189,1399,612,676]" pageId="112" pageNumber="113">
The specimens from 
<collectingCountry box="[446,517,612,638]" name="Nepal" pageId="112" pageNumber="113">Nepal</collectingCountry>
differ from the description of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Barkalov &amp; Cheng" authorityYear="2004" box="[890,1086,612,638]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="112" pageNumber="113" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="suspecta" subGenus="Cheilosia">
<emphasis box="[890,917,612,638]" italics="true" pageId="112" pageNumber="113">C.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[937,964,612,638]" italics="true" pageId="112" pageNumber="113">C.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[983,1086,613,638]" italics="true" pageId="112" pageNumber="113">suspecta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by having dark colour of basoflagellomere in both male and female, dark-orange with darkened marigin in the original description.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
